Name: Jawaharlal Nehru Botanical Garden
Description: A lush green expanse featuring a variety of plant species, including many species of Orchids.

Name: Shanti View Point
Description: Offers a panoramic view of the surrounding hills and valleys, a serene spot for photography.

Name: Ganesh Tok
Description: A small temple dedicated to Lord Ganesha, located on a hill that provides breathtaking views of Gangtok.
